name: Sakshi
content: Tesla is one of the world's most valuable companies in terms of market capitalization. In October 2021, Tesla temporarily became a trillion-dollar company, the seventh U.S. company to do so. In 2023, the company led the battery electric vehicle market, with 19.9% share.

name: Sakshi
content: From the iconic Tata Tea to Tata Motors' electric vehicles, the Tata Group continues to transform industries and uplift communities. Let's celebrate their legacy of excellence!
